    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Spirit)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 1</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 26 | <b>Successes:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 14 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 30</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Highly forbidden in most villages, this technique lets you scramble your own Chakra Signature to become unrecognizable, or change it into one of a creature you are familiar with, as long as you both are of the same type (and subtype). A creature that senses your Signature can make a Wisdom check (DC 18) to look past the deception.</p>\n\n\n\n",
